data.description: Pride of ownership shines in this fantastic 2,563 s.f. 4 bed/2 bath single level home w/ bonus room in the coveted Thousand Springs Sub!  The curb appeal is instantly charming w/ craftsman details, perfect proportions, & beautiful landscaping.  Inside, the open entry foyer greets you with extensive trimwork & draws you into the generous living space complete w/ cozy gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings, ample daylight as well as new carpet & paint throughout!  Functionality is highlighted by the split bedroom plan w/ central living spaces, a double door office @ the entry, as well as the large bonus room over the 3 car garage.  The back yard is NW facing complete w/ a large covered patio, mature trees, a 2nd patio off the Master, and potential for dog run on the side of the home.  Set quietly away from traffic yet walking distance to Gordon Harris Park.  Other features include NEW AC (2019), Furnace (2019), Water heater (2021), tray ceilings in the Office & Master, and a large laundry room w/ sink & storage.
